my-endwise.vim

my-endwise.vim is improved endwise.vim. ( http://www.vim.org/scripts/script.php?script_id=2386 )
my-endwise.vim solves problem which occurs when <CR> is rekeymaping and <CR> is input with endwise.vim.

You must set <CR> keymap for push back "<Plug>DiscretionaryEnd".

example:
    [before] inoremap <expr><CR>  pumvisible() ? neocomplcache#smart_close_popup()."\<CR>" : "\<CR>"

    |
    V

    [after]  imap <buffer> <expr><CR>  pumvisible() ? neocomplcache#smart_close_popup()."\<CR>\<Plug>DiscretionaryEnd" : "\<CR>\<Plug>DiscretionaryEnd"

